      "definition": "The process of creating and managing a distinct identity, image, and perception for an organization or product in the minds of customers.",
      "what_it_really_means": "Positioning expressed through visual identity, voice, and experience. Branding is how positioning is made tangible and recognizable. A strong brand makes positioning visible at every customer touchpoint.",
