      "definition": "A response to a challenge or opportunity that is designed to strengthen long-term competitive position rather than only address the immediate situation.",
      "what_it_really_means": "A solution that improves the strategic position rather than just solving the presenting problem. Strategic solutions ask whether the fix also moves the organization toward or away from an advantageous competitive position.",
      "why": "Points to Advantageous Positioning. A strategic solution is one designed to reinforce or create advantageous positioning.",
      "alternatives": [],
