      "what_it_really_means": "The one thing that makes the case for choosing this over everything else. A USP only holds when the distinction is genuine, valued by the customer, and not easily replicated. Many claimed USPs are not unique, not selling, and not a point.",
      "why": "Points to Positioning. A unique selling point is the defining element of a competitive position.",
