      "what_it_really_means": "The best case articulated as financial or commercial potential. When product-market fit is achieved, upside potential becomes accessible. Before it is achieved, upside potential is speculative.",
      "why": "Points to Product-Market Fit. Upside potential is the outcome that becomes realizable once product-market fit is established.",
