      "status": "alternative",
      "primary": "360 Feedback",
      "formula_type": null,
      "formula": "See: 360 Feedback",
      "components": [],
      "definition": "A performance review format in which feedback is collected from all directions — manager, peers, direct reports, and self — to provide a complete view of an individual's performance.",
      "what_it_really_means": "The same concept as 360 Feedback. The degree framing emphasizes the full circle of perspectives gathered. Both terms describe the same multi-source feedback approach.",
