      "what_it_really_means": "The meeting that should drive decisions but often just reviews slides. A real QBR produces something on the other side of it: a changed priority, a confirmed commitment, a decision that would not have been made otherwise. A QBR that ends without those things is a progress report dressed up as a strategy session.",
