      "what_it_really_means": "The capabilities that do not appear in a job description but determine whether someone is effective in the role. Soft skills — communication, empathy, adaptability, influence — are increasingly recognized as hard to develop and hard to replace.",
      "why": "Points to Skills Matrix. Soft skills are a category within the skills matrix alongside technical or hard skills.",
