      "what_it_really_means": "The document that answers the question nobody wants to ask out loud: what happens if that person leaves tomorrow. A succession map done honestly is uncomfortable. It reveals gaps. Organizations that do it well treat those gaps as a development priority. Organizations that do it poorly treat the map as a compliance document.",
