      "why": "Ratio formula. The ratio shifts constantly. The goal is not a fixed split but a relationship between the two sides that remains sustainable over time. When work demands consistently outpace personal time and energy, the ratio breaks down. Naming it as a balance suggests it can be found and held. The truth is it has to be actively managed.",
