      "why": "Sequential experience stages and emotional and behavioral data at each stage are grouped because the journey map delivers its value through both layers simultaneously. Stages without emotional data show what happened. Emotional data without sequential stages shows feelings without context. Together they produce a narrative of the experience that is both structured and human.",
