      "what_it_really_means": "An SOP applied to a specific context. Protocols are common in healthcare, safety, and technology — they establish the exact steps to follow in defined situations to ensure consistency and safety.",
      "why": "Points to SOP. A protocol is a specific type of standard operating procedure applied to defined high-stakes interactions.",
