      "why": "Ratio formula expressed as elapsed time. Investment or adoption without the first value delivered defines a start with no endpoint. First value without the elapsed time produces a milestone with no measure of how long it took. Together they define time to value as a complete measurement from commitment to benefit, making it actionable for product design, onboarding, and investment planning.",
