      "why": "All three components carry equal weight. Total revenue is the aggregate. All revenue streams captures the breadth of sources contributing to it. Gross sales before deductions clarifies that the top line is the gross figure — before returns, discounts, and allowances are removed. Together they define the top line as the full incoming revenue before any subtractions.",
